| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3093 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7a08b9c4-5dd1-54a6-8d3c-4d5352150b2e"
